<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="yesterday-n">yesterday <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'jestədeɪ, 'jestədi/    美 /'jestərdeɪ, 'jestərdi/  </p>
<p>[U]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>昨天：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>the day before yesterday</strong>
前天</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>yesterday morning / afternoon / evening 
昨天上午/下午/晚上</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Yesterday will not be called again. 
昨日一去不复返。</p></div></div>